    answer: "Both require sales conversations. Docebo's average contract value is approximately $40,000/year. Sana Labs starts at $8–$13/user/month with a 300-user minimum, putting the annual floor at approximately $28,800–$46,800. At comparable scale, both land in similar territory: roughly $50,000–$80,000+ annually."
  },
  {
